title: Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit
text:
> Washington Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit Gary Shamblin of Winston, Ore., prepares to leave a parking lot in Roseburg, Ore., on Thursday Oct. 8, 2015, in his 1934 International truck displaying a sign he made reflecting his views on President Barack Obama's planned visit to the area.
